structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.history: Repealed Ky. Acts ch. 172, sec. 91. -- Amended 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 57, sec. 2. -- Created 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 176, sec. 12.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Sale or transfer of property in unapproved subdivision prohibited; contracts and conveyances void.
